    },
    {
      "text": "Let's Yoga (どこでもヨガ, Doko Demo Yoga) is a fitness video game developed by Vanpool and published by Konami for the Nintendo DS. It was released in Japan on July 5, 2007, Europe on November 16, 2007, and in North America on April 29, 2008.\nLet's Yoga features 25 main yoga lessons for the user to complete, and functions as an interactive yoga workout guide for the player. The game was released concurrently with Let's Pilates, a game also developed by Vanpool. It has received a 76.67% from GameRankings.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Let's Yoga è un videogioco fitness sviluppato da Vanpool e pubblicato da Konami per il Nintendo DS. È uscito in Giappone il 5 luglio 2007, in Europa il 16 novembre 2007 e in Nord America il 29 aprile 2008.\nIl videogioco è stato distribuito in concomitanza con Let's Pilates, anch'esso sviluppato da Vanpool.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Let's Yoga（どこでもヨガ）』は、Vanpoolが開発し、コナミが発売したニンテンドーDS用フィットネスビデオゲームです。日本で2007年7月5日、ヨーロッパで2007年11月16日、北米で2008年4月29日に発売されました。\n\n本作は、ユーザーが完了する25のメインヨガレッスンを特徴とし、プレイヤーのためのインタラクティブなヨガワークアウトガイドとして機能します。同作は、同じくVanpoolが開発した『Let's Pilates』と同時に発売されました。GameRankingsでは76.67%の評価を獲得しています。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
